%% Diagram: Transactionally-staged job drain
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant API as API
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant ENQ as Enqueuer
    participant Q as Redis
    participant W as Worker

    API->>DB: BEGIN
    API->>DB: INSERT ride
    API->>DB: INSERT staged_jobs
    API->>DB: COMMIT

    Note over DB: rows visible to<br/>other transactions

    loop poll
        ENQ->>DB: BEGIN (REPEATABLE READ)
        ENQ->>DB: SELECT staged_jobs LIMIT N
        ENQ->>Q: ENQUEUE jobs
        ENQ->>DB: DELETE selected
        ENQ->>DB: COMMIT
    end

    Q-->>W: dequeue
    W->>W: send receipt
